::Cledar/Forrior/Blyer/Rixer/Firearm::

Cledar sees that Windlord was talking to someone else, and walks back to his troops. "Allright, Rixer, go back to the city for repairs. Me, Forrior, and Blyer will go to the IGL to see if we can register late. We'll meet you after the competition."

Rixer nods, turning and moving off toward Maximal City. Blyer opens his cockpit, Cledar and Forrior climbing in. He jets off toward the IGL.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Firearm looks around, seeing that there was no one to fight, and also setting off toward the IGL, wanting to watch or participate if he could join late.
